Congrats!

I'm sure we've all heard the old joke of grad students discussing which is
the better high level programming language. One says C, another says
Pascal, a third Lisp. The professor walks in and settles it by saying "the
best high level programming languange is a grad student". No you'll have
your own!

cheers,
mattias
